The Veteran's Memorial Building is internationally renowned for its Yoga and Pilates classes as well as church services, community meetings, and various multi-cultural weddings. The attached theater is currently in use as the primary stage for the ["Davis Senior High School"] drama department until the new Performing Arts Center is constructed (see DSHS page).

Veterans Memorial Building (sometimes refered to as Veterans Memorial Theater/Center) is located adjacent to ["Davis Senior High School"], on 203 East ["14th St."]

The building was dedicated Febuary 24th 1974.
